# Gemini Chat - Flow Walkthrough

อธิบาย Flow การทำงานตั้งแต่ Frontend -> Backend -> Database -> Gemini API

---

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Frontend
        A[GeminiChat.vue] --> B[useGeminiChat.ts]
    end
    subgraph Backend
        C[index.ts - API Routes]
        D[service.ts - Business Logic]
        E[gemini-client.ts - AI Client]
